<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Application <%= status === 'approved' ? 'Approved' : 'Update' %></title>
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f7; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .header { padding: 32px; text-align: center; color: #ffffff; }
    .header-approved { background: #16a34a; }
    .header-rejected { background: #6b7280; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 24px; }
    .body { padding: 32px; color: #333333; line-height: 1.6; }
    .body h2 { margin-top: 0; color: #1a1a1a; }
    .reason-box { padding: 16px; background: #f9fafb; border-left: 4px solid #d1d5db; border-radius: 4px; margin: 16px 0; color: #374151; }
    .cta { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 32px; background: #16a34a; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; }
    .footer { padding: 24px 32px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #888888; border-top: 1px solid #eee; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header <%= status === 'approved' ? 'header-approved' : 'header-rejected' %>">
      <h1><%= status === 'approved' ? 'Application Approved!' : 'Application Update' %></h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <h2>Hi <%= consultantName %>,</h2>

      <% if (status === 'approved') { %>
        <p>Congratulations! Your application for the project <strong><%= projectTitle %></strong> has been approved.</p>
        <p>You are now a member of this project. You can start collaborating with the team right away.</p>

        <% if (projectUrl) { %>
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 24px 0;">
          <a href="<%= projectUrl %>" class="cta">View Project</a>
        </div>
        <% } %>
      <% } else { %>
        <p>Thank you for your interest in the project <strong><%= projectTitle %></strong>.</p>
        <p>After careful review, the project owner has decided not to proceed with your application at this time.</p>

        <% if (rejectionReason) { %>
        <div class="reason-box">
          <strong>Feedback:</strong><br />
          <%= rejectionReason %>
        </div>
        <% } %>

        <p>We encourage you to continue exploring other projects that match your skills.</p>
      <% } %>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; <%= year %> Marketplace. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
